body_html:
I am not super familiar with the hub scripts, but someone will take a look at that issue soon as well.

I believe you are using a version of the retrain.py script that doesn't yet have support for the proper quantized models.

This is the version of the code you should be using and the line that recognizes '_quant': https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.8/tensorflow/examples/image_retraining/retrain.py#L1022

Please make sure you are using that version.

I am not super familiar with the hub scripts, but someone will take a look at that issue soon as well.

I believe you are using a version of the retrain.py script that doesn't yet have support for the proper quantized models.

This is the version of the code you should be using and the line that recognizes '_quant': https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.8/tensorflow/examples/image_retraining/retrain.py#L1022 

Please make sure you are using that version.
